reviewText: Very disappointed with the quality of this DVD it came from the UK and it will not play in my DVD player I tried contacting the company and got no response

Probably Bette Davis' best performance. A cliff hanger movie. If you have not seen this movie, you will never expect the ending. This was Davis' first movie after marrying Gary Merrill and "all About Eve."
Hard to find Bette Davis movie.  One of my favorites of hers.  This is one of those Amazon dvd's on demand and it was great.  No issues with it at all.

I love this movie and was very excited about obtaining a copy on DVD.
The excitement was short lived.  The quality of the copy is not the best.  It is very dark during various scenes.
